metadata.name: Is it a Bubble?
metadata.description:
This piece of artwork is called "Is it a bubble" in which i have created a portrait inside a bubble, showing one face with multiple personalities.

Sometimes thats the feeling we get, when we cant express the real thing we are feeling but begin to lie about it but in reality we are feeling completely different.
Thats the main idea of this painting, And heavily Inspired by the Movie Bladerunner 2049.

Process is available at : www.twitter.com/classypaints
